    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Wrecking Ball grapples into the enemy backline to trigger Minefield or Piledriver, scattering the enemy formation so his own team can clean up the disorganized fight that follows.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>His value is almost entirely disruption rather than personal kill power, so against a team that just regroups after the initial scatter, he contributes little sustained pressure.</p>"
